title: Trailer Trash #5 (Restored)
description:
Restored to better than original condition

I have decided to redo the recent uploads which were faithful reproductions on crappy paper that has yellowed with age. This new lot which have 'restored' in the title have been cleaned up with jet black and clean white as far as possible without clogging up any of the fine hatching or blowing any of the type. It looks as if it has been printed on high quality paper. I'll probably end up redoing the whole lot.
